                <h1>After Ferguson shooting, nearly half of Americans don’t believe in justice – poll</h1>

                <div class="cont-wp-mid max_width">
                    <div class="acticle_clock">
						<!-- time -->
                        <span class="time">
                            Published time: August 15, 2014 10:38                                                            <br>
                                Edited time: August 16, 2014 11:10                                                    </span>
                        <!--// time -->
						
                        <div id="get-short-url">
                            <a href="" class="get" data-url="http://rt.com/usa/180508-poll-police-black-huffington/">Get short URL</a>
                            <div class="url"></div>
                        </div>
                       <div class="i-clears i-mh"></div>  
                        
                    </div>
                  <div class="i-clears i-mh"></div>
                    
                  <div class="article_img" style="float: none; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom:10px;">
                    <img title="" src="http://img.rt.com/files/news/2c/11/c0/00/rtr42hvi.si.jpg"
                         alt="People sit on a car as it drives by a peaceful demonstration, as communities react to the shooting of Michael Brown in Ferguson, Missouri August 14, 2014. (Reuters / Mario Anzuoni)"
                         style="float: none; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px;">
                                        <p class="article_img_footer">People sit on a car as it drives by a peaceful demonstration, as communities react to the shooting of Michael Brown in Ferguson, Missouri August 14, 2014. (Reuters / Mario Anzuoni)</p>
                                      </div>

                  <div style="overflow:hidden">
                    <script type="text/javascript" src="//s7.addthis.com/js/300/addthis_widget.js#pubid=ra-5396eb96220e676a"></script>

<!-- Go to www.addthis.com/dashboard to customize your tools -->
